==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Calorificient
<hw>Ca*lor`i*fi"cient</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Having, or relating to the power of producing
heat; -- applied to foods which, being rich in carbon, as the fats, are
supposed to give rise to heat in the animal body by oxidation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

